*** WORK IN PROGRESS ***

1. To build (or rebuild) sample code:

mvn clean install

2. To start a fresh test server:

cd integration
mvn -Dsling.clean -Dsling.start clean install

3. To stop the test server:

mvn -Dsling.stop install

4. To create some test content:

curl -u admin:admin -F "sling:resourceType=myberkeley/scriptedsample" -F title="Some Title"  http://localhost:8080/content/firstscriptedsample

5. To try the Groovy script:

curl http://localhost:8080/content/firstscriptedsample.json

6. To try the server-side Javascript script:

curl http://localhost:8080/content/firstscriptedsample.html

